{
  "texts": [
    "Strategy for ChatGPT accuracy improvementRecent studies have found that transformer-based language models can greatly enhance response accuracy by generating answers in a stepwise manner.",
    "This is made possible by the LLM's ability to predict the following word based on prior context.",
    "To achieve this, it is necessary to prompt a sufficiently large LLM to generate responses step by step.",
    "In our research, we have improved the prompt by explicitly indicating the domain of questions or requesting the LLM to explain its reasoning process before providing an answer.",
    "Table 1 showcases various types of prompts that were utilized.For the OpenAI model, the domain-specific aspect is included in the system prompt, while the explanation prompt is in the user prompt."
  ]
}